pyseas-cad includes a small pure-Python triangulation compatibility module at
src/cad/_vendor/earcut.py.

The public API is intentionally compatible with the common mapbox-earcut
`triangulate_float32(vertices, hole_indices, dimensions)` shape used by Python
ports. The implementation in this repository is original Stage 1 code and is
licensed under the same terms as pyseas-cad.

